query:
insert into transactions (
                id,
                user_id,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                date,
                categorize_on,
                amount,
                currency,
                counter_party,
                additional,
                notes,
                account_id,
                category_id
            )
            select 
                $1, $2::text, $3, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, $9, $10,
                (select id from accounts where id = $11 and user_id = $2::text),
                (select id from transaction_categories where id = $12::text and user_id = $2::text)
